'''蕾吉娜·伊莉妮琪娜·史派克特'''（{{lang-en|Regina Ilyinichna Spektor}}，{{lang-ru|link=no|Реги́нa Ильи́нична Спе́ктор}}，{{bd|1980年|2月18日||catIdx=Spektor, Regina }}）<ref name="Contact">{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/regina-spektor |title=Regina Spektor | Biography, News, Photos and Videos |publisher=Contactmusic.com |date= |accessdate=2015-08-24 |archive-date=2017-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170726174544/http://www.contactmusic.com/regina-spektor |dead-url=no }}</ref>，擁有[[猶太|猶太]]血統，是一位出生在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的[[美國|美國]]女歌手<ref>{{cite web|first=Eva|last=Wiseman|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2016/nov/13/regina-spektor-the-only-reason-im-jewish-is-antisemitism|title=Regina Spektor: ‘The only reason I’m Jewish is antisemitism’|work=The Guardian|date=November 13, 2016|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142833/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2016/nov/13/regina-spektor-the-only-reason-im-jewish-is-antisemitism|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==簡介==
[[File:Regina_Spektor_black_and_white.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Regina_Spektor_(2006).jpg|thumb]]
蕾吉娜·史派克特1980年2月18日出生在[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]（現[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]）[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的[[猶太人|猶太人]]家庭<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2016/10/03/496125426/regina-spektor-i-see-my-family-in-everybody|title=Regina Spektor: 'I See My Family ... In Everybody'|work=National Public Radio|date=October 3, 2016|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517153000/https://www.npr.org/2016/10/03/496125426/regina-spektor-i-see-my-family-in-everybody|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Ben|last=Harris|url=https://www.jta.org/2012/04/02/arts-entertainment/amid-mainstream-success-regina-spektor-stays-true-to-jewish-roots|title=Amid mainstream success, Regina Spektor stays true to Jewish roots|work=JTA - Jewish news|date=April 2, 2012|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517223422/https://www.jta.org/2012/04/02/arts-entertainment/amid-mainstream-success-regina-spektor-stays-true-to-jewish-roots|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蕾吉娜·史派克特是一名出生於音樂世家的[[女歌手|女歌手]]、[[作曲|作曲]]人和[[鋼琴家|鋼琴家]]。

居住在蘇聯莫斯科的時候，由於猶太人面臨種族歧視和政治歧視，所以她的猶太父母決定要移民<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2012/08/27/160106266/regina-spektor-on-growing-up-a-soviet-kid|title=Regina Spektor: On Growing Up A 'Soviet Kid'|work=National Public Radio|date=August 27, 2012|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517152819/https://www.npr.org/2012/08/27/160106266/regina-spektor-on-growing-up-a-soviet-kid|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Ryan|last=Torok|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/85787/|title=Regina Spektor goes live|work=Jewish Journal|date=December 8, 2010|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517223228/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/85787/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Jenny|last=Eliscu|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/new-yorks-screwball-pop-queen-20090709|title=New York's Screwball Pop Queen|work=Rolling Stone|date=July 9, 2009|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517153730/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/new-yorks-screwball-pop-queen-20090709|dead-url=no}}</ref>；在1989年（蕾吉娜·史派克特9歲時）她和家人離開莫斯科，一家人移民到美國並在紐約州[[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]定居<ref>{{cite web|first=Lane|last=Billings|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/blogs/lists/2012/06/10-awesome-things-about-regina-spektor.html|title=10 Awesome Things About Regina Spektor|work=Paste magazine|date=June 2, 2012|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517152855/https://www.pastemagazine.com/blogs/lists/2012/06/10-awesome-things-about-regina-spektor.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Dean|last=Budnick|url=https://www.relix.com/articles/detail/parting_shots_regina_spektor|title=Parting Shots: Regina Spektor|work=Relix magazine|date=January 4, 2017|accessdate=May 17, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517223420/https://www.relix.com/articles/detail/parting_shots_regina_spektor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的父親是一名攝影師，也是一名業餘的[[小提琴|小提琴]]手，她的母親原是一名俄羅斯音樂學院的音樂教授，現在任教於美國紐約的一所公立小學。

蕾吉娜·史派克特6歲習琴，創作受到多種風格的影響。近年來，她活躍於紐約的反傳統民謠（Anti-Folk）圈子內，這是一種源於80年代美國的音樂流派。

